title: Hip Hop Hits The Hottest Hip Hop Of The Year 2008 3 cds Resource

Hip Hope Hits 2008: The Hottest Positive Hip Hop of the Year

Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Whether you are looking for the classic hitmakers like tobyMac, Grits and John Reuben or if you are looking for the up and comers from Shonlock and Group 1 Crew, Hip Hope Hits 2008 has them all. 
This CD includes 3 exclusive songs from Family Force 5, The DIverse City Band and Gabe Real of Diverse City Band.
